A police officer has been shot and killed and another wounded after responding to a complaint on Tuesday night. CAPE TOWN - A police officer has been shot and killed and another wounded, after they were attacked in Philippi.The two were responding to a complaint on Tuesday night when they were attacked by three armed men.The wounded official is in a critical, but stable condition in hospital.The suspects fled the scene with the officers' firearms.(Edited by Shimoney Regter)